title: Apache OpenOffice 4.0.1 [Portable - Multilingual!] [trckryou]
description:
This is latest release of Apache OpenOffice 4.0.1, but this one is Portable!
I did reupload this because of slow download from the site.

Originaly released by: OpenOffice/WinPenPack!

Languages included: English, French, German, Italian, Spanish


How to install:
---------------
1. Download the zip and extract to your USB/HDD
2. Open X-ApacheOpenOffice.exe
3. Wait for it to run, and that's all!

Enjoy, and seed! :)
